'''Hicham Boudaoui''' ({{langx|ar|هشام بوداوي}}; born 23 September 1999) is an Algerian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[Ligue 1]] club [[OGC Nice|Nice]] and the [[Algeria national football team|Algeria national team]].

==Club career==
On 6 January 2018, Boudaoui made his professional debut for Paradou AC, coming as a second-half substitute in a league match against [[USM Alger]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://us.soccerway.com/matches/2018/01/06/algeria/ligue-1/paradou-athetic-club/union-sportive-madinet-dalger/2537073/|title=Paradou AC vs. USM Alger - 6 January 2018 - Soccerway|publisher=Soccerway|date=6 January 2018|access-date=29 November 2018}}</ref>

In September 2019, he joined [[Ligue 1]] side [[OGC Nice|Nice]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Hicham Boudaoui, the latest Aiglon |url=https://www.ogcnice.com/fr/actualite/37715/hicham-boudaoui-the-latest-aiglon |website=OGC Nice |access-date=24 December 2019 |date=2 September 2019}}</ref>

==International career==
Boudaoui made his debut for the [[Algeria national football team|Algeria national team]] on 27 December 2018 in a friendly against [[Qatar national football team|Qatar]], as a starter.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[Eurosport]]|url=https://www.eurosport.com/football/international-friendlies/2018/live-qatar-algeria_mtc1088937/live.shtml|title=Qatar v Algeria game report|date=27 December 2018}}</ref> He was named in Algeria's national team squad for the [[2019 Africa Cup of Nations]] in Egypt.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dzfoot.com/2019/05/30/can-2019-les-23-algeriens-pour-legypte-152787.php|title=CAN 2019 : Les 23 Algériens pour L'Egypte|author=Mohamed B|publisher=DZfoot|language=fr|date=30 May 2019|access-date=10 June 2019}}</ref>

In December 2023, he was named in Algeria's squad for the [[2023 Africa Cup of Nations]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.algerie-focus.com/can-2024-lalgerie-devoile-sa-liste-officielle-qui-sont-les-fennecs-prets-a-conquerir-lafrique/|title=CAN 2024 : L'Algérie Dévoile sa Liste Officielle – Qui Sont les Fennecs Prêts à Conquérir l’Afrique ?|language=French|date=30 December 2023|access-date=12 January 2024|publisher=Algérie-Focus}}</ref> He has also appeared for [[Algeria national under-20 football team|Algeria U20]] and [[Algeria national under-23 football team|Algeria U23]] teams.

